snippet.title: Barbie Fashion Closet App Preview + Scrapbooking & New Extra Doll
snippet.description:
Hi Fashionistas! We’ve got a fresh new look with some awesome new features for you:
- Introducing the Scrapbook: Snap a pic, decorate it with fun stickers, then share it with your friends!
- Make way for the newest Barbie Extra character bringing her fabulous fashions to the closet!
- Bunches of new fashions and accessories to try out!
